text: Kaya tumhi kanagostipurvi dana karanyasa bhyale tara jevha tumhi ase kele nahi ani allahane dekhila tumhala mapha kele tevha ata (ucitapane) namajanna kayama rakha, jakata deta raha ani allaha ani tyacya paigambaracya adesace palana karita raha ani tumhi je kahi karata te sarva allaha (cangalya prakare) januna ahe
